Package: pollster
Title: Interface to the Huffpost Pollster API
Description: An R interface to the Huffington Post Pollster API, which provides
    programatic interface to political polls.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Jeffrey B.", "Arnold", email = "jeffrey.arnold@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
